#: ../../i18n.rst:2 c546cc5e27bd4ef2a81311ee5999d5a9
msgid "Internationalization (i18n)"
msgstr "Internationalisation (i18n)"

#: ../../i18n.rst:4 6d6f5a56168a4c868fa70498e6162a85
msgid ""
"RansomLook's web UI supports multiple languages through `Flask-Babel "
"<https://python-babel.github.io/flask-babel/>`_. The project currently "
"ships **English** (source language) and **French** translations."
msgstr ""
"L'interface web de RansomLook prend en charge plusieurs langues via "
"`Flask-Babel <https://python-babel.github.io/flask-babel/>`_. Le projet "
"fournit actuellement des traductions en **anglais** (langue source) et "
"**français**."

#: ../../i18n.rst:9 1d43a986d8594d4dbd1e70155bd9b056
msgid "How the locale is chosen"
msgstr "Comment la locale est choisie"

#: ../../i18n.rst:11 5d9b4eb0c0e643e3ac66857518ce8742
msgid "On every request the active locale is picked in this order:"
msgstr "À chaque requête, la locale active est choisie dans cet ordre :"

#: ../../i18n.rst:13 dda4e40f0f2245e481a82b5e7d4f20ad
msgid ""
"**``locale`` cookie** — set by the user when they click the ``EN / FR`` "
"switcher in the top bar. Persisted for one year."
msgstr ""
"**Cookie ``locale``** — posé par l'utilisateur quand il clique sur le "
"switcher ``EN / FR`` de la barre du haut. Persisté un an."

#: ../../i18n.rst:15 e1078ba49f1849ceb8574b2008bc3ae8
msgid ""
"**Browser ``Accept-Language``** — when no cookie is set, the best match "
"against the list of available locales is used."
msgstr ""
"**``Accept-Language`` du navigateur** — sans cookie, on prend la "
"meilleure correspondance avec les locales disponibles."

#: ../../i18n.rst:17 5ad46f0f86d74070bc281695dae7d5a4
msgid "**Fallback** — ``en``."
msgstr "**Fallback** — ``en``."

#: ../../i18n.rst:20 b7b751835b17408094ee1dc9474cd8d0
msgid "Switching language on demand"
msgstr "Changer de langue à la demande"

#: ../../i18n.rst:22 1590a6b5c26f4309ad8ebaf4d4fc5f73
msgid ""
"Hitting ``/set-locale/<code>`` (for example ``/set-locale/fr``) sets the "
"cookie to the requested locale and bounces back to the referrer. The top-"
"bar switcher is just a pair of links to those endpoints."
msgstr ""
"Appeler ``/set-locale/<code>`` (par exemple ``/set-locale/fr``) pose le "
"cookie sur la locale demandée et redirige vers la page d'origine. Le "
"switcher de la barre du haut est simplement une paire de liens vers ces "
"endpoints."

#: ../../i18n.rst:27 635de341c9b3492283475c3a7d044abf
msgid "File layout"
msgstr "Arborescence"

#: ../../i18n.rst:39 5105348b10984f0ca11dcfa9ec50b090
msgid ""
"Flask-Babel loads the ``.mo`` files at process start. You **must "
"restart** the web server (gunicorn / development runner) after "
"recompiling for changes to take effect."
msgstr ""
"Flask-Babel charge les fichiers ``.mo`` au démarrage du processus. Il "
"faut **redémarrer** le serveur web (gunicorn / runner de dev) après "
"recompilation pour que les changements prennent effet."

#: ../../i18n.rst:43 ff3d98f083784cd69660a55680c483b0
msgid "Workflow for contributors"
msgstr "Workflow pour les contributeurs"

